title: Gorgeous Cedar Park property, $99 App & Admin
posting_body: Located in the south end of Cedar Park, with quick access to Hwy 45 and Hwy 183 and a mile from Lakeline's MetroRail station, this community is incredibly accessible and will provide you with convenient access to the greater Austin area, while keeping you away from the hustle and bustle of the city.
This lush, pet-friendly community has gorgeous views and amazing amenities.

On the property, you'll have outdoor grilling stations, a beautiful pool, pet park, 24-hour fitness center with on-site trainers, a large clubhouse, and many community spaces great for social gathering!

The unit itself has washer and dryer included, walk-in closets, outside patio storage, and amazing kitchens with deep sinks, granite countertops, a microwave, garbage disposal, and dishwasher included.
There's so much more available in this amazing community.
Pricing and Availability subject to change.
